import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom"

// const root = React.DOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))

ReactDOM.render(
  <BrowserRouter>
  <App />,
  {document.getElementById('root')}
  </BrowserRouter>
)
